{"tid":637324,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"當黃子華棟篤笑成為熱話 仲有無人記得張達明...","createTime":"2018-04-21T16:48:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-22T03:58:02.000Z","uid":19208,"like":1,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"16dd10ce54ca66ef96b7e1e32d0ee40866e0e7b0","tid":637324,"uid":19208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T16:48:50.000Z","msg":"張達明中學畢業後就讀香港演藝學院，與黃秋生成為同學，1988年戲劇系畢業。1995年與黃子華合作演出棟篤笑而被觀眾認識，並向喜劇演員的方向發展。他亦嘗試在表演中混合棟篤笑與戲劇的元素，其「形體動作」如扮速龍等令觀眾印象深刻。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>棟篤笑</strong><br />\n<br />\n1994年及1995年：《麻甩騷》<br />\n<br />\n1995年：《棟篤笑雙打之玩無可玩》(與黃子華合演)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UZOP5TXoS10\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DUZOP5TXoS10&d=hxg47QoceM5mP1F6l8fP6pZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=f489d7b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UZOP5TXoS10</a><br />\n<br />\n1998年：《鬚根Show》(與黃子華、吳鎮宇合演)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PqVFvEIQKeU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DPqVFvEIQKeU&d=hxg47QoceM5mP1F6l8fP6pZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=4e6fa71f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PqVFvEIQKeU</a><br />\n<br />\n2000年：《香港藝術節一咀Show之蓄意縱火》、《鬚根Show 2》<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HlfNYaLwDpM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DHlfNYaLwDpM&d=hxg47QoceM5mP1F6l8fP6pZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=438815c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HlfNYaLwDpM</a><br />\n<br />\n2001年：《兩篤笑》(與吳君如合演)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bUtlneKJe8Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DbUtlneKJe8Q&d=hxg47QoceM5mP1F6l8fP6pZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=5af7a229\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bUtlneKJe8Q</a><br />\n<br />\n2008年：《大珠三角篇 之人仔無敵》<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=b73Ev07to7c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Db73Ev07to7c&d=hxg47QoceM5mP1F6l8fP6pZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=461e9959\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=b73Ev07to7c</a><br />\n<br />\n2011年：《一於做壞旦》<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DlOFB4IjPCA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DDlOFB4IjPCA&d=hxg47QoceM5mP1F6l8fP6pZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=01709d16\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DlOFB4IjPCA</a>"},{"pid":"b7a816f17e376f0d3ba82398da9492cf2fa27efd","tid":637324,"uid":126133,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T16:50:28.000Z","msg":"佢自己一個唔好睇"},{"pid":"dae2dba9ad50dee3e85e2393f05618fbc0afb6eb","tid":637324,"uid":19208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T16:52:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://timable.com/res/pic/98afd6001401fdd8efb1b4d32c6270742.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftimable.com%2Fres%2Fpic%2F98afd6001401fdd8efb1b4d32c6270742.jpg&h=d766cc64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.episo.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/press_CTM_poster20110308.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.episo.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2014%2F02%2Fpress_CTM_poster20110308.jpg&h=0570ae7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://timable.com/res/pic/005dc38e25cccddfaa6bc410e0ee553a2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftimable.com%2Fres%2Fpic%2F005dc38e25cccddfaa6bc410e0ee553a2.jpg&h=6021ec7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.tradeduck.com/uploads/68837_11030619.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tradeduck.com%2Fuploads%2F68837_11030619.jpg&h=f026c963&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://luilongting.files.wordpress.com/2016/02/ming4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fluilongting.files.wordpress.com%2F2016%2F02%2Fming4.jpg